        {
            "title": "美國總統｜特朗普在社交媒體發文 要求聯儲局馬上減息 高盛：料減息推遲至九月",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/U2uIM8tQPhbM9GwR3AClwQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/d516a53fb5ef968480fbbd06ad2d34f1\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然特朗普總統已經提名新任<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯儲局\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲局;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲局\">聯儲局</a>主席，但他周四（12日）在社交媒體要求聯儲局主席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鮑威爾\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:鮑威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鮑威爾\">鮑威爾</a>馬上減息，但有投資銀行認為隨着伊朗局勢緊張，預計最快下半年才會開始減息周期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普星期四在社交媒體發文要求聯儲局主席鮑威爾馬上減息，直言「應該立刻減息，不要等到下次會議」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原本市場預期今年有機會全年減息三次，但因應中東衝突爆發，情況可能略為不同。聯儲局將於下周二至下周三（17日至18日）召開議息會議，但市場估計維持利率不變的機率為99.1%。甚至預期9月仍可能維持不變，12月減息的機率為六成。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f5dc74b8-a1fe-35be-a516-1615ebfb2ffe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資銀行高盛預期今年減息將會推遲至九月，今年最多減息兩次，因為現時中東局勢緊張加上通脹仍然高企，將會推遲減息周期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨着現任主席鮑威爾在今年五月卸任，特朗普已經提名沃什作為新任聯儲局主席，甚至早前在訪問中表示若履行職責（does the job that he’s capable），美國經濟增長率可望達到15%。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%9C%A8%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E5%B1%80%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%8A%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-%E6%96%99%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF%E6%8E%A8%E9%81%B2%E8%87%B3%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88-100238342.html",
